WEBVTT

00:00:08.860 --> 00:00:10.830
You’re on the trail of a werewolf

00:00:10.830 --> 00:00:12.810
that’s been terrorizing your town.

00:00:12.810 --> 00:00:14.780
After months of detective work,

00:00:14.780 --> 00:00:17.640
you’ve narrowed your suspects to 
one of five people:

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:18.500
the mayor,

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:19.390
the tailor,

00:00:19.390 --> 00:00:20.200
the baker,

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:21.295
the grocer,

00:00:21.295 --> 00:00:22.645
or the carpenter.

00:00:22.645 --> 00:00:25.350
You’ve invited them to dinner 
with a simple plan:

00:00:25.350 --> 00:00:28.410
you’ll slip a square of 
a rare werewolf antidote

00:00:28.410 --> 00:00:30.110
into each of their dinners.